# Pre-registration directory — what is committed and what is local-only.
#
# COMMITTED (no leading bang needed; tracked by git):
#   - amendment_phase15.md           — phase-amendment narrative
#   - preregistration_lock.json      — operator-filled confirmatory lock
#                                      (template lives in this repo as well;
#                                      operator overwrites it locally before a
#                                      confirmatory run)
#
# IGNORED (operator-private notes that must NOT travel into a published lock):
*.private.md
*.private.json
*.draft.md
*.draft.json
notes_*.md
